ttings":{"include_margins":true}},"666031d5-a46e-4066-b3a6-6c08af22965f":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19690677403972__666031d5-a46e-4066-b3a6-6c08af22965f-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3>Elke oplader die je nodig hebt in mooi design<\/h3><p><\/p><p>Je kan nu al je <strong>Apple<\/strong> apparaten <strong>4X sneller <\/strong>opladen met 1 strak uitziende, draadloze oplader, zonder het gedoe van allemaal in de knoop zittende draden. De <strong>ROOLO <\/strong>draadloze oplader zijn al jouw apparaten zo weer terug naar 100% batterij. Snel en efficiënt.<\/p><ul><li>Exclusief en Modern Design<\/li><li>Gratis Snel Opladen (3.0 adapter)<\/li><li>Gratis verzending + 30 dagen bedenktijd<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["template--19690677403972__666031d5-a46e-4066-b3a6-6c08af22965f-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}},"ba4b200c-5189-42f4-94c4-72222e7552a1":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/oplaadstation_png_maken.webp","height":"medium","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"0c0525d8-4497-4085-979f-a13f8432a51e":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19690677403972__0c0525d8-4497-4085-979f-a13f8432a51e-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h2><\/h2><ul><li><strong>INNOVATIEF: <\/strong>Het 3-1 ontwerp zorgt ervoor dat al je apparaten op één plek blijven, zodat je 's ochtends niet hoeft te zoeken. <\/li><li><strong>STRAK<\/strong>: Het ontwerp geeft al je apparaten genoeg ruimte om op een stijlvolle en compacte manier op te laden. <\/li><li><strong>3 IN 1:<\/strong> Het opladen houdt al je apparaten gereed voor gebruik.<\/li><li><strong>SMART: <\/strong>Sensoren detecteren automatisch je apparaat en laten met LED's zien dat het is verbonden.<\/li><\/ul>"}}},"block_order":["template--19690677403972__0c0525d8-4497-4085-979f-a13f8432a51e-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":52}},"e1ab7d57-6e66-4beb-9c34-7002b553f53c":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/video_oplaadstation_1.webp","height":"medium","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"60b34cf8-6e04-4b5d-bbd8-82ccbf135e92":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19660118655300__60b34cf8-6e04-4b5d-bbd8-82ccbf135e92-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>Geen Kabel Bende<\/strong><\/h3><p>Dankzij de ROOLO Draadloze oplader zal je geen last meer hebben van die rommel aan kabels naast je bed. In plaats daarvan kan je genieten van één strakke oplader voor al je apparaten.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19660118655300__60b34cf8-6e04-4b5d-bbd8-82ccbf135e92-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":52}},"e8cb6fcc-4da5-4d26-8027-5634bd9f62ff":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--19690677403972__e8cb6fcc-4da5-4d26-8027-5634bd9f62ff-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h1>🔋<\/h1><p>SNEL LADEN! <br\/>Laad je apparaten binnen 1 uur op.<\/p><h1>🔌<\/h1><p>Alle laders die je nodig hebt in één apparaat, geen los hangende kabels meer.<\/p><h1>🧲<\/h1><p>Laad veilig je apparaten op, plaats eenvoudig je telefoon aan de oplader en het verbind automatisch met je batterij.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--19690677403972__e8cb6fcc-4da5-4d26-8027-5634bd9f62ff-text-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/oplaadstation3zwartachter.webp","height":"medium","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"center"}},"64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-1":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Handig","icon":"star","row_content":"<p>Onze oplader zorgt ervoor dat je geen problemen meer hebt met loshangende kabels.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-2":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Krachtig","icon":"lightning_bolt","row_content":"<p>Met de 15 watt aan stroom wat onze oplader kan bieden is jouw telefoon en andere accessoires snel opgeladen🔋<\/p>","page":""}},"template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-3":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Draai Functie","icon":"recycle","row_content":"<p>Draai je telefoon op de gewenste stand, zodat je eenvoudig kan Facetimen of Film kijken terwijl je telefoon aan het opladen is.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-4":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Stijlvol","icon":"heart","row_content":"<p>Naast dat de ROOLO Charger 3 verschillende apparaten snel kan opladen, is het ook een mooie toevoeging aan je huis of kantoor.<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-1","template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-2","template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-3","template--19660118655300__64750dde-6c31-486e-a24f-4c8fc1e07447-collapsible_row-4"],"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h1","h